Dortmund sensation Haaland could be a cheaper alternative for Real Madrid instead of Kylian Mbappe, writes @Marca. With PSG not agreeing to negotiate for Mbappe - Real Madrid needs to look at an alternative and Haaland's &euro;75m release clause next year makes him the favorite.<br />
<br />
BVB could be open to selling Haaland if a high offer arrives this summer. Now, it's up to Madrid and Florentino if they want to wait until closer to 2022 to sign Mbappe, or go for Haaland before then. Having Odegaard already at the club would help him settle in nicely. [<br />
@Marca<br />
]

